Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:02.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get crackin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:03.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's-a-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:05.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:36.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't put on my uniform in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:38.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:39.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:44.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:47.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A very good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Tsukasa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:54.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ribbon is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:56.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna hurl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:00.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:04.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have become hooked on Marimite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Marimite?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:10.06,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,222)}Image
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start copying their costumes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:15.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that called cosplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:23.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already do plenty of that at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:24.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You work at one of those places...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:29.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Kona-chan was a high-class lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feels so wrong that I can't even picture it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Baseball games have been going over schedule too much recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do the people watching new anime get shafted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to watch anime that badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:48.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you could get cable or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there specialized channels for that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,God knows I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the cable guys were all like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get cable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:06.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look kinda down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I went to have my cavity taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:20.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there so many follow-up trips after a visit to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't just one or two trips!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:27.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:35.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuki-chan's so amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.78,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm pleased to see you looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's talking the same way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but it doesn't feel weird at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she isn't even questioning the way Kona-chan's talking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:49.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen a person say "good day" in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be a regularly used greeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the girls' school my friends go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A real school for rich girls is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...told me to collect summer homework for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seba—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Butlers must be named Sebastian, do you not agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You do get that impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Tell us a funny story, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.11,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\i1}Ain't happening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Vacation just ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you ain't got no time to be mooching around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:25.95,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(542,219)}Schedule\Nfor\NSecond Semester
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Start thinking about your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and put effort into studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:29.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By future, she means choosing a major?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess high school is only a temporary stopping point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:35.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you probably haven't done\Nmuch thinking about the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:36.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:37.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose liberal arts to be in the\Nsame class with everyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:43.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsu-Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You blabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.72,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Ah, sorries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you told her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...o-of all people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:51.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just been honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You hate being lonely, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For my summer homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:16.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did as you told me and wrote down\Nrandom stuff when I didn't know the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now I have to redo it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:26.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get help from me, you might have to redo it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you know what I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:27.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She got out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An extension on homework without\Nan extension on summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should borrow Kagami's notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of cicadas puts me to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The schedule's off because the baseball game went over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can be useful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My recorder's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:21.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your glasses, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They broke this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that I left them on the chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but could I borrow your notes for today later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still got the clumsy thing going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:43.13,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(555,290)}Konata's Notes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Konata-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:43.15,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(118,305)}Bad handwriting\Nthat can't be read
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your handwriting is a mystery to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.80,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(561,287)}Tsukasa's Notes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsukasa-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.80,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(117,345)}So detailed that\Nshe didn't get\Neverything down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:51.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:56.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing we have the same teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But please keep this a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wish to ruin their good intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:11.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me use your notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected Yuki-chan to borrow my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:22.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.71,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,30)}STARE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In games, when a character who wears\Nglasses shows up at school without them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...they suddenly become popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that doesn't happen in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It really doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't chocolate cornets kinda look like drills?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Drills...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:52.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Didn't we discuss which side of a chocolate cornet was the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how the thin end looked like the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the fat end looks more like the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one big bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And layers of stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When the lower half of your body gains weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it becomes difficult to buy skirts and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use your waist measurements, you can't get it over your hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:16.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If it fits your hips perfectly, it's loose around your waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice but to buy one that's too big for your waist...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and when you walk around in it\Nyour skirt starts spinning, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:23.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A body with layers of stomach looks like a cornet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn it on the side...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can play it like a cornet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn it again, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...put it on your head like a cornet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that supposed to be funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:39.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you dieting to make up for the added summer weight, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But my weight went down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...without my waist or hips changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the fruits of your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's plain to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:57.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that when you diet you lose\Nweight in the places you don't want to first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.35,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When reading literature...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.06,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...the trick is to keep the theme in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.88,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...and understand what the author is trying to convey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:14.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that people with poor eyesight end up\Nwith nasty expressions that scare other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it depends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said it depends on the person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you glanced over at me, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:25.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that thinner eyes make you look prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:28.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you look more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:31.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:32.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:41.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:42.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Way late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:46.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who's always complaining\Nabout night games lasting too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...shouldn't be so loose with time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:52.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All the games have been going over schedule lately so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it infected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it's contagious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:55.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:57.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Overslept?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:58.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give me an adult reason for why you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:10.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There was still plenty of time left when I finished getting ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So to kill time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I started playing games and couldn't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:14.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worse than a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:16.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:21.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of cultural festivals and\Nsporting events during second semester, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have tests soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:27.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan is really athletic so she can do well in sporting events.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like sporting events 'cause they make me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:34.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty rare to see such an athletic sit-inside-all-day type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what our class will do for the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything I'd want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...can never be decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...unless someone wants to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the person who brings up the idea usually gets put in charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so nobody's willing to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:52.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have to stay after school to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to watch evening anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to cook dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have to stop by the store on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:12.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's favorite chicken curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in our family loves chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:21.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that letting curry sit overnight makes it taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It works well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:27.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll make some extra and bring it for lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there'll be leftovers anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:31.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Hiiragi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:35.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The curry I made yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I let it sit overnight and it's spoiled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry usually doesn't go bad in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you put in anything weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:54.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was mold in it this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Another cornet today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They taste good so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the difference between when your lunches are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.04,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(78,144)}Mini Hamburger Patties
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.04,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(59,239)}Fried Eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.04,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(62,356)}Bacon Sauté\Nwith broad beans and onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.04,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(63,448)}Salted Asparagus\Nand Carrots
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.04,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(518,39)}Made Properly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...made properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or made frugally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.91,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(115,40)}Made Frugally
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.91,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(532,192)}Grilled Salmon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.91,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(544,319)}Okra\N(Just boiled and sliced)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.91,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(537,373)}Pickled Vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.91,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,433)}And nothing else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is really obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:18.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ts-Tsukasa and I take turns making lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with housework...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It always ends up being simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry it's frugal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:31.85,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,394)\frz36.012}Oh boy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:26.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the type of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:30.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...who can blow up pots when they cook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody in the world can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan's lunch looks wonderful again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's lunch is just leftovers from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dinner at Miyuki-san's place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is really fancy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And these are just the leftovers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:52.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside these fried eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We had some eel leftover last night so I added it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't usually see leftovers for eel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that's ever leftover at our house is moldy curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your house isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They bought me a cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:18.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I did well on my practical exams for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what my number was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:26.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.12,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}You have a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I usually forget it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Dad's the only one who ever calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that defeat the purpose of having a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:06.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:07.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keroro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:08.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:12.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They bought it for me with the cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a girl in our class who\Nhad a bunch of straps on her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They weighed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the straps alone were 800 grams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:22.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's heavy, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she took the straps off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...her stiff shoulders were cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:30.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like making a phone call would count as weight training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:36.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it exciting how you never know\Nwhen you'll get a call on your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope someone calls me soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to get so excited over a cell phone nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:46.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you find your number yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:48.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:49.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In England...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:53.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was a large struggle between the\NHouse of Lancaster and the House of York.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:58.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The two houses fought wearing red and white roses respectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, this war was known as the War of Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:05.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It lasted from 1455 to 1485.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:06.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody finally called me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick it up in the faculty office after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But junk mail already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking with Konata and Miyuki and lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little late and look what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:53.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with Kona-chan and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think he'd get the idea after calling one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fathers are always worried about their daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure get a lot of junk mail these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:19.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to make your address hard to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My e-mail address is in roman letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,iluvgiriswithglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go with maids or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But maids and shrine maidens are popular and easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We get it already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:38.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so don't talk so loudly around the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your conversation is a bigger problem than the junk mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My cell phone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She left it in her pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone to a better place, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll buy me another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenacious little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the e-mail last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:20.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that said Kagami wanted her notes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last one you sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.06,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You never respond immediately when you get an e-mail, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:33.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't reply to people I can talk to whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Reply to e-mails through e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We see each other every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to lose your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that big a deal anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't decide that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:49.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she didn't return my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:57.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:04.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:08.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This manga I borrowed from Kona-chan moved me to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the manga, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it so stupid and hilarious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:18.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It moved me to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it hard to believe you're talking about the same manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cry, you're with Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you laugh, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be classified with either of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanna see how Sis reacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it wrong to want to know more about your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:37.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Attack No. 1 make you cry or laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.64,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's your favorite manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sgt. Frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.81,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Sgt. Frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't tell if these two are similar or not...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join a manga club, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you love manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd be willing to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd be a good use of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw. Draw. Draw. Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you even try on this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:06.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Konata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this a picture of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I could really stretch and say that you captured her spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can breathe fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits Kagami-san's image so perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a frightening child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a new volume of FMP out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I guess there's a release date coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading to Gamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just stop by a local bookstore today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some other stuff to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:44.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to come with me as a sign of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:45.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are clingy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you shouldn't be using words like friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:55.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to give me your\Npurchase points as a sign of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:59.05,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(514,27)}I can almost get the item I want
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your idea of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.05,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}You've waited so long for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's quiet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:13.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she mad about how I mixed up the\Nribbons on my pigtails with sunflowers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:19.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To Akira-sama?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:24.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:27.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It started already...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:31.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No choice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before they change the channel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wanted to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we're on another episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:42.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minoru Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama's in a bad mood so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You said your own name before the name Akira Kogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not understand what natural order is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:02.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like those pigtails of yours have been\Ngetting ridiculously popular in certain places.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't call it popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be getting full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:09.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:14.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People were expecting Project\NFashionable Akira to show me in pigtails, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:15.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with twin drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:21.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Twin drills?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't underestimate the Getter's speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 2, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The age of pigtails is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The new thing is twin drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what Konata said?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drills are like a man's romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:34.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can catch the rest of this on\Nthe radio show and our home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look forward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:42.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:45.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About those pigtails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the ones I had?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones in the real life picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:50.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:51.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You had sunflowers on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:52.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That looked awfully familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:55.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:56.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}How many years ago was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.77,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}H-Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}In one of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:58.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eew! Eew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:06.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cute and wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:10.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it so nerve-wracking when you're singing your first song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You wonder if your voice can be heard and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki's next, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:16.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing us something full of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:19.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have the mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:20.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:21.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:25.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm not used to this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:27.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me if it offends your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:28.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:29.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:38.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This ties in to the other Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:47.97,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,PLEIADS IS IN THE WIND.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:52.85,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MILKY WAY IS IN THE SAND.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:56.73,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,WHERE HAS EVERYONE GONE?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:23:02.44,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I NEVER SAID GOODBYE.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:07.19,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,PEGASUS IS IN THE PRAIRIE.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:12.07,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,VENUS IS ON THE STREET CORNER.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:15.83,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,WHERE HAS EVERYONE GONE?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:21.33,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,i CAN NO LONGER WATCH OVER THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:26.09,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,NOBODY REMEMBERS THE STARS ON THIS PLANET.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:29.68,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,PEOPLE ALWAYS LOOK UP AT THE SKY.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.51,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,38)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:49.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even her singing is manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:52.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a new kind of turn-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:54.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool, Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukasa.
